WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

2
00:00:52.874 --> 00:00:54.292
Tomorrow.

3
00:00:54.292 --> 00:00:57.254
Bring him to the fields

4
00:00:57.254 --> 00:00:59.798
to work and it'll be okay.

5
00:01:58.315 --> 00:01:59.566
Ah Niu!

6
00:02:29.388 --> 00:02:31.348
Ah Niu. Ah Niu. Ah Niu!

7
00:02:31.348 --> 00:02:33.433
Come with me. come with me!

8
00:02:33.433 --> 00:02:35.977
Go. come. follow me!

9
00:02:37.354 --> 00:02:40.148
You see. all the work you did during
the day is for nothing.

10
00:02:40.148 --> 00:02:42.025
Aunt Yue Ci won't let us say anything.

11
00:02:42.025 --> 00:02:44.695
But she's helping you redo it.

12
00:03:03.422 --> 00:03:05.340
Seedlings have life too.

13
00:03:05.340 --> 00:03:07.718
They can't stay too close

14
00:03:07.718 --> 00:03:10.512
or it will hinder growth.

15
00:03:10.512 --> 00:03:11.847
Just like us humans.

16
00:03:11.847 --> 00:03:14.099
In life. we must respect each other

17
00:03:14.099 --> 00:03:16.935
That way we can live
peacefully and happily.

18
00:03:19.187 --> 00:03:21.106
I'll remember that.

19
00:05:14.845 --> 00:05:16.054
Grandma. lets eat.

20
00:05:16.054 --> 00:05:17.222
Sure.

21
00:05:23.770 --> 00:05:25.147
Grandma.

22
00:05:25.147 --> 00:05:26.898
Yue Ci.

23
00:05:26.898 --> 00:05:28.400
Grandma.

24
00:05:28.692 --> 00:05:31.653
In a couple of days. it'll be time
to pay respects at the cemetery.

25
00:05:31.653 --> 00:05:33.739
Go to the cemetery.

26
00:05:33.739 --> 00:05:35.907
to pay respect to your parents.

27
00:05:35.907 --> 00:05:37.743
Okay.

28
00:05:45.208 --> 00:05:49.004
Grandma told me. in a couple of days
I should go and visit my parents' graves.

29
00:06:29.252 --> 00:06:30.587
Drink some water.

30
00:06:37.552 --> 00:06:39.429
I would like to discuss
something with you.

31
00:06:41.973 --> 00:06:43.392
You're leaving?

32
00:06:48.605 --> 00:06:50.399
I would like to take a trip back.

33
00:06:50.649 --> 00:06:52.984
also to pay respects to my dead parents.

34
00:06:54.319 --> 00:06:57.447
Filial piety is important. you should go.

35
00:07:35.777 --> 00:07:37.654
I'll be coming back again.

36
00:07:43.452 --> 00:07:45.620
You've been here for many years.

37
00:07:45.620 --> 00:07:50.375
I knew that one day you would
eventually leave this place.

38
00:07:50.584 --> 00:07:52.586
Actually I...

39
00:08:02.721 --> 00:08:06.683
These are a change of clothes for
your journey.  Please take it.

40
00:08:10.896 --> 00:08:13.482
I haven't told you my name yet.

41
00:08:15.108 --> 00:08:17.402
You need not tell me.

42
00:08:17.402 --> 00:08:20.489
Where you came from.
or where you're going.

43
00:08:20.489 --> 00:08:23.200
I need not know either.

44
00:08:23.200 --> 00:08:27.371
I'm just need to know you as Ah Niu.

45
00:08:31.291 --> 00:08:33.960
My name is Huo Yuan Jia.

46
00:09:15.669 --> 00:09:17.587
I'll remember it.

47
00:10:03.300 --> 00:10:09.056
1907. Tian Jin

48
00:10:34.164 --> 00:10:39.044
Here's something good to eat.
- Here's something good to eat.

49
00:10:43.340 --> 00:10:45.258
Word of God is trust!

50
00:10:45.258 --> 00:10:47.219
Trust the God and receive eternal life!

51
00:10:47.219 --> 00:10:48.595
Really. really!

52
00:10:48.595 --> 00:10:50.514
Trust the God and receive eternal life!

53
00:10:50.514 --> 00:10:53.058
His words are all in here!

54
00:10:53.058 --> 00:10:54.935
God's words are here!

55
00:11:22.337 --> 00:11:24.256
Huo Yuan Jia!

56
00:11:25.465 --> 00:11:27.217
Number one in Tian Jin!

57
00:11:27.217 --> 00:11:29.720
Huo Yuan Jia!

58
00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:31.138
Number one in Tian Jin!

59
00:11:31.138 --> 00:11:34.433
Huo Yuan Jia!

60
00:11:34.433 --> 00:11:35.892
Huo Yuan Jia

61
00:11:35.892 --> 00:11:38.979
Came back!

62
00:11:39.479 --> 00:11:41.857
Huo Yuan Jia came back to fight
the arenas again!

63
00:12:25.692 --> 00:12:29.237
Master!
- Uncle Lai Fu.

64
00:12:29.237 --> 00:12:30.489
You're back!

65
00:12:30.489 --> 00:12:33.909
Good. let me carry it for you.

66
00:13:04.272 --> 00:13:07.859
Sorry. I failed in my duties in taking
care of your family assets

67
00:13:07.859 --> 00:13:10.904
Master. I'm sorry.

68
00:13:32.926 --> 00:13:37.264
I'm always thinking of the day
Master returns.

69
00:13:37.264 --> 00:13:41.435
All the things in here.
nothing has been changed.

70
00:13:43.186 --> 00:13:45.355
It's been hard on you.

71
00:13:45.355 --> 00:13:47.399
It's my duty.

72
00:13:47.399 --> 00:13:48.650
Master.

73
00:13:48.650 --> 00:13:53.864
After you left. the creditors came
here everyday for the debts.

74
00:13:53.864 --> 00:13:59.036
All the things in the house.
were taken by them one by one.

75
00:13:59.036 --> 00:14:04.041
In the end. they even wanted the
house to pay off the debt

76
00:14:04.624 --> 00:14:09.379
All of the things in this room
were able to be kept intact.

77
00:14:09.379 --> 00:14:13.967
only because someone
sent us a sum of money.

78
00:14:13.967 --> 00:14:16.011
After much thought.

79
00:14:16.011 --> 00:14:23.143
I believe the only person who
could have done this is
Nong Jing Shun. Master Nong.

80
00:14:34.321 --> 00:14:36.573
I don't need them any more.

81
00:14:38.533 --> 00:14:42.454
I believe my parents also don't wish
to see these things again.

82
00:14:45.874 --> 00:14:48.210
Honorable Father. I was a bad son.

83
00:14:48.585 --> 00:14:54.299
Only now do I realise.
that year on the stage

84
00:14:54.424 --> 00:14:55.467
why you didn't deliver the final blow.

85
00:14:56.134 --> 00:15:00.847
You. are the real number one in Tian Jin.

86
00:15:02.224 --> 00:15:04.184
Honorable Mother.

87
00:15:04.184 --> 00:15:08.397
You taught me moral values in the past.

88
00:15:08.397 --> 00:15:11.942
Your son was too foolish
and didn't understand it back then.

89
00:15:14.820 --> 00:15:16.029
Don't worry.

90
00:15:17.072 --> 00:15:21.243
I will not disappoint you again.

91
00:15:25.747 --> 00:15:28.208
My child.

92
00:15:28.208 --> 00:15:32.838
I didn't take good care of when
you were still alive.

93
00:15:32.838 --> 00:15:36.383
and I even brought such a great
misfortune on you.

94
00:15:38.468 --> 00:15:40.887
I'm not a good father.

95
00:16:02.242 --> 00:16:07.247
Madam. in the past I've wronged
Master Qin.

96
00:16:07.789 --> 00:16:11.543
Today I've come to pay my
respects to Master Qin.

97
00:16:26.350 --> 00:16:31.480
Mum! Mum!

98
00:16:46.328 --> 00:16:47.371
Extra! Extra!

99
00:16:47.371 --> 00:16:50.749
A strong foreigner. O'Brien has swept
the fighting scene in Asia.

100
00:16:50.749 --> 00:16:52.542
With 32 consecutive wins.

101
00:16:52.542 --> 00:16:55.337
25 challengers seriously injured.

102
00:16:55.670 --> 00:17:00.842
He is invincible! He ridiculing the
Chinese as "Sick Man of Asia."

103
00:17:00.842 --> 00:17:03.929
But no one dares to challenge him.

104
00:17:05.514 --> 00:17:07.099
Jing Sun.

105
00:17:09.184 --> 00:17:11.186
I've done you wrong.

106
00:17:11.937 --> 00:17:15.315
There are many things that.
only after they happened.

107
00:17:15.315 --> 00:17:17.984
does one realize that they were wrong.

108
00:17:18.151 --> 00:17:21.613
The wrong pains my heart deeply.

109
00:17:21.613 --> 00:17:24.449
I don't want to mention the past again.

110
00:17:24.449 --> 00:17:26.618
It's over now.

111
00:17:33.208 --> 00:17:34.334
Jing Sun.

112
00:17:34.835 --> 00:17:36.503
It's hard for me to ask.

113
00:17:36.712 --> 00:17:38.630
But you're my only hope.

114
00:17:38.964 --> 00:17:40.841
I need to borrow some money.

115
00:17:41.049 --> 00:17:43.760
Still going to fight in the arena?

116
00:17:44.094 --> 00:17:45.637
Yes.

117
00:17:46.763 --> 00:17:49.057
I don't have such a friend like you.

118
00:17:49.266 --> 00:17:51.643
Why should I lend you the money?

119
00:18:40.150 --> 00:18:41.693
Master.

120
00:18:41.902 --> 00:18:43.153
Boss Huo.

121
00:18:43.153 --> 00:18:46.031
This is a gift from my master.

122
00:18:49.201 --> 00:18:51.203
Who is your master?

123
00:18:51.203 --> 00:18:55.499
He's Nong Jing Sun.

124
00:18:59.920 --> 00:19:03.215
1909. Shanghai Racetrack

125
00:19:15.852 --> 00:19:17.771
Ladies and gentleman.

126
00:19:17.771 --> 00:19:21.733
The person appearing before you today

127
00:19:21.733 --> 00:19:25.028
can single-handedly move a train.

128
00:19:25.028 --> 00:19:28.115
with a single blow. can punch
a hole through the Great Wall of China.

129
00:19:28.115 --> 00:19:29.074
What bullshit!

130
00:19:29.074 --> 00:19:34.162
with his little finger. he can squeeze
a Chinese fighter to death!

131
00:19:35.080 --> 00:19:36.540
Sucker!
- Introducing.

132
00:19:36.540 --> 00:19:39.251
The strongest man we've ever seen.

133
00:19:39.251 --> 00:19:42.421
O'Brien!

134
00:20:06.945 --> 00:20:09.531
The challenger for today.

135
00:20:09.531 --> 00:20:13.326
Huo Yuan Jia from Tian Jin!

136
00:20:17.414 --> 00:20:20.292
Great!

137
00:20:35.432 --> 00:20:37.392
Sign the agreement first.

138
00:20:38.769 --> 00:20:39.770
Tell him.

139
00:20:40.645 --> 00:20:42.856
Fighting to the death

140
00:20:42.856 --> 00:20:44.983
Has always been China's bad practice.

141
00:20:44.983 --> 00:20:47.152
But we have another tradition.

142
00:20:47.152 --> 00:20:49.237
It is making friends through competition.

143
00:20:49.237 --> 00:20:52.240
Nice!

144
00:21:07.214 --> 00:21:07.881
Come on!

145
00:21:07.881 --> 00:21:10.384
Let the competition officially begin!

146
00:21:19.976 --> 00:21:20.852
Come on!

147
00:21:26.233 --> 00:21:27.150
Come on!

148
00:21:28.944 --> 00:21:29.903
All right!

149
00:21:51.842 --> 00:21:54.177
Good!

150
00:22:36.261 --> 00:22:37.971
Good!

151
00:24:06.018 --> 00:24:07.310
All right!

152
00:24:08.270 --> 00:24:12.816
Well done. Master Huo!

153
00:24:13.734 --> 00:24:15.318
With respect.

154
00:24:45.849 --> 00:24:47.267
Thank you.

155
00:24:51.813 --> 00:24:56.485
Great.

156
00:25:22.219 --> 00:25:24.096
"Shanghai Foreign Journalists Club"

157
00:25:28.475 --> 00:25:32.396
Master. someone invited you.

158
00:25:38.360 --> 00:25:42.072
Jing Sun. I didn't expect it to be you.

159
00:25:43.156 --> 00:25:44.908
You still treat me as a friend?

160
00:25:44.908 --> 00:25:47.411
There's no way I can forget you. my friend.

161
00:25:47.994 --> 00:25:49.454
No way.

162
00:25:51.331 --> 00:25:54.418
Come. have a seat. Yuan Jia.

163
00:25:55.252 --> 00:25:58.255
I've prepared your favourite wine.

164
00:25:58.255 --> 00:26:02.009
Come!

165
00:26:02.009 --> 00:26:03.468
What's the matter.

166
00:26:03.468 --> 00:26:04.469
I've quit drinking.

167
00:26:04.469 --> 00:26:05.846
It's been many years now.

168
00:26:05.846 --> 00:26:08.098
You were so fond of drinking in the past.

169
00:26:08.098 --> 00:26:11.101
It is for the sake of righting the wrongs
in my past.

170
00:26:12.894 --> 00:26:14.730
Good.

171
00:26:14.938 --> 00:26:18.233
Then. we'll use tea in place of the wine.

172
00:26:26.366 --> 00:26:27.826
Yuan Jia.

173
00:26:27.826 --> 00:26:31.955
Your fight. has gained back great
self-esteem to our countrymen.

174
00:26:31.955 --> 00:26:34.458
The Westerners have forced us this far.

175
00:26:34.458 --> 00:26:37.377
And there should be a Chinese
to stand up for us.

176
00:26:37.377 --> 00:26:39.087
As a friend.

177
00:26:39.171 --> 00:26:41.465
I'm really happy for you.

178
00:26:41.465 --> 00:26:44.509
Please try some.

179
00:26:50.390 --> 00:26:51.558
Jing Sun.

180
00:26:51.558 --> 00:26:53.602
When are you leaving this time?

181
00:26:53.602 --> 00:26:56.188
Since I've come. I'm not leaving.

182
00:26:57.481 --> 00:26:59.399
What about your restaurant?

183
00:27:00.817 --> 00:27:01.860
I sold it.

184
00:27:01.860 --> 00:27:03.445
Sold it?

185
00:27:03.445 --> 00:27:05.489
The business was very good. wasn't it?

186
00:27:05.489 --> 00:27:07.949
You want to start the Jing Wu School.

187
00:27:07.949 --> 00:27:10.786
How are you going to do it without money?

188
00:27:10.786 --> 00:27:14.664
But the restaurant was all your life's work.

189
00:27:14.664 --> 00:27:16.458
If compared with your goal.

190
00:27:16.458 --> 00:27:20.170
My insignificant restaurant business is nothing.

191
00:27:20.545 --> 00:27:21.922
Yuan Jia.

192
00:27:21.922 --> 00:27:24.633
I'm not a practitioner of martial arts.

193
00:27:25.050 --> 00:27:30.389
I can only contribute this little amount.

194
00:27:30.722 --> 00:27:32.224
To help you on your road to success.

195
00:27:38.480 --> 00:27:41.316
These regulations are according to the content we discussed.

196
00:27:42.859 --> 00:27:44.569
Please check if you're okay with it.

197
00:27:46.905 --> 00:27:50.409
Jing Wu School has three ideals.

198
00:27:50.575 --> 00:27:54.246
Educate the Body. Mind and Morals.

199
00:27:53.537 --> 00:27:56.206
Martial arts is a way to strengthen oneself.

200
00:27:56.206 --> 00:27:57.165
Regardless of different sects or schools.

201
00:27:58.208 --> 00:28:02.587
By exchanging and interacting with
one another to understand the essence.

202
00:28:01.878 --> 00:28:04.631
With a strong body. and a clear mind

203
00:28:04.631 --> 00:28:08.552
Our countrymen can renew and strengthen themselves.

204
00:28:08.552 --> 00:28:11.513
Do not use your fists to harm your countrymen.

205
00:28:11.513 --> 00:28:12.931
Do not abuse martial arts.

206
00:28:12.931 --> 00:28:16.226
Virtue and morality are the basics.

207
00:28:16.226 --> 00:28:18.770
Constantly strive to become stronger!

208
00:28:20.313 --> 00:28:21.565
1910. Official Founding of Jing Wu School.

209
00:28:22.774 --> 00:28:25.444
Ready!

210
00:28:28.864 --> 00:28:30.115
Shanghai Foreign Traders Associate

211
00:29:52.280 --> 00:29:53.615
Yuan Jia.

212
00:29:54.991 --> 00:29:56.368
Among the competitors this time.

213
00:29:56.368 --> 00:29:59.329
There is a Japanese by the name
of Tanaka Yasuno.

214
00:29:59.329 --> 00:30:00.914
He would like to meet you.

215
00:30:00.914 --> 00:30:05.794
I heard that he is one of the best
among all the experts.

216
00:30:07.421 --> 00:30:10.507
We can only learn something if we
spar with the best.

217
00:30:10.507 --> 00:30:13.760
Yuan Jia. this competition organised
by the foreigners.

218
00:30:13.760 --> 00:30:15.637
I don't think it's that simple.

219
00:30:15.637 --> 00:30:16.763
How come they're getting you

220
00:30:16.763 --> 00:30:19.683
to fight four people consecutively
all on your own?

221
00:30:19.683 --> 00:30:23.854
I believe they're trying to use this
opportunity to humiliate us.

222
00:30:23.854 --> 00:30:28.233
To make the Jing Wu School lose
its standing in Shanghai.

223
00:30:28.608 --> 00:30:30.235
Yes.

224
00:30:30.235 --> 00:30:33.572
Not only is it one against four. but I'm also
required to win every single match.

225
00:30:33.572 --> 00:30:36.825
It is definitely unfair.

226
00:30:37.200 --> 00:30:38.952
But in life.

227
00:30:39.411 --> 00:30:43.582
who can guarantee that everything
is going to be fair?

228
00:30:45.625 --> 00:30:47.169
For Jing Wu School.

229
00:30:49.171 --> 00:30:51.089
I have no other option.

230
00:30:51.089 --> 00:30:52.549
But what if.

231
00:30:53.592 --> 00:30:55.635
Jing Sun.

232
00:30:56.011 --> 00:30:57.554
I need to discuss something with you.

233
00:30:57.554 --> 00:30:59.306
What is it?

234
00:30:59.556 --> 00:31:01.099
After this match.

235
00:31:01.099 --> 00:31:03.310
I want you to replace me as president.

236
00:31:03.310 --> 00:31:06.313
Why?

237
00:31:06.521 --> 00:31:09.649
I want to spend some time to go back and
visit Yue Chi and her grandma.

238
00:31:10.150 --> 00:31:12.027
I promised them.

239
00:31:20.702 --> 00:31:25.874
So. from what you said. do you really
not know anything about the art of tea?

240
00:31:26.958 --> 00:31:30.003
It's not that I don't understand. I'm just
unwilling to understand.

241
00:31:30.712 --> 00:31:33.632
I don't want to categorise the tea.

242
00:31:33.632 --> 00:31:35.008
As long as it's tea it'll be fine with me.

243
00:31:35.300 --> 00:31:41.306
But tea also has differences in quality and grade.

244
00:31:41.515 --> 00:31:44.559
What is considered good?
And what is considered bad?

245
00:31:45.477 --> 00:31:48.980
They all grow in nature.

246
00:31:49.189 --> 00:31:51.066
There is no good or bad.

247
00:31:51.066 --> 00:31:52.693
It seems you really don't understand.

248
00:31:52.693 --> 00:31:55.737
Otherwise you'll definitely come to
realise which is good and which is bad.

249
00:31:55.737 --> 00:31:57.447
You're also right.

250
00:31:57.447 --> 00:31:59.700
So from my perspective

251
00:31:59.700 --> 00:32:01.576
The quality of the tea

252
00:32:01.576 --> 00:32:04.454
is not determined from the tea itself.

253
00:32:04.454 --> 00:32:06.498
It is decided by man.

254
00:32:06.498 --> 00:32:09.167
Different people have different choices.

255
00:32:09.167 --> 00:32:11.336
I'm unwilling to make this choice.

256
00:32:11.336 --> 00:32:14.339
Oh. why?

257
00:32:14.339 --> 00:32:16.466
Enjoying tea is simply depends on your mood.

258
00:32:16.466 --> 00:32:18.844
As long as you're in a good mood.

259
00:32:19.219 --> 00:32:22.180
Is the quality of the tea still that important?

260
00:32:22.180 --> 00:32:24.683
Oh. I have never thought of it this way.

261
00:32:25.100 --> 00:32:29.271
From your perspective. there are so many
different schools and factions of martial arts.

262
00:32:29.271 --> 00:32:33.316
Is there really no distinction between superior
and inferior ones?

263
00:32:33.525 --> 00:32:35.736
I think that's the case.

264
00:32:36.236 --> 00:32:40.032
Then. I would like to ask you.

265
00:32:40.032 --> 00:32:42.701
Since there is no distinction of superior or
inferior kinds in martial arts.

266
00:32:42.701 --> 00:32:44.995
Why do we still improve by competing with one another?

267
00:32:44.995 --> 00:32:50.083
I believe that there really is no
such distinction in martial arts.

268
00:32:50.167 --> 00:32:53.545
The difference only lies in the ability of the practitioner.

269
00:32:53.545 --> 00:32:56.214
Through the competition we can
discover

270
00:32:56.214 --> 00:32:58.425
and get to know one's true self.

271
00:32:58.425 --> 00:33:00.510
Because our real opponent

272
00:33:00.510 --> 00:33:02.721
may be still our self.

273
00:33:02.721 --> 00:33:07.017
Only through competition.
can one recognise one's true self.

274
00:33:07.017 --> 00:33:08.894
Is it possible that you mean.

275
00:33:08.894 --> 00:33:15.275
the most significant fight is within oneself?

276
00:33:22.074 --> 00:33:27.996
Your words have gained my sincere respect.

277
00:33:29.331 --> 00:33:31.875
Today we're here to make friends.
through this tea appreciation.

278
00:33:31.875 --> 00:33:35.253
Let's not keep talking and forget about the tea.

279
00:33:35.253 --> 00:33:37.255
Come. appreciate the tea.

280
00:33:37.255 --> 00:33:38.548
Appreciate the tea.

281
00:33:44.137 --> 00:33:48.308
"1910 .Shanghai"

282
00:33:52.145 --> 00:33:55.399
"Theater Biarya. France Constitution"

283
00:33:56.817 --> 00:33:59.861
"Match Venue"

284
00:34:07.077 --> 00:34:08.412
Ladies and gentlemen

285
00:34:08.412 --> 00:34:10.080
The last fight of the day is.

286
00:34:10.080 --> 00:34:12.874
Tanaka Yasuno from Japan

287
00:34:12.874 --> 00:34:15.961
against Huo Yuan Jia from China's Jing Wu School.

288
00:34:16.753 --> 00:34:18.797
What's all this about?

289
00:34:19.923 --> 00:34:22.342
Four against one?

290
00:34:23.468 --> 00:34:25.345
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

291
00:34:25.595 --> 00:34:27.139
This is what the Trader's Associate

292
00:34:27.389 --> 00:34:29.266
and the Jing Wu School agreed upon.

293
00:34:29.266 --> 00:34:30.934
You need not be surprised.

294
00:34:30.934 --> 00:34:34.104
You call this a competition?

295
00:34:34.438 --> 00:34:36.106
This is murder.

296
00:34:36.106 --> 00:34:38.859
You worry too much Tanaka-kun.

297
00:34:38.859 --> 00:34:40.610
Huo Yuan Jia has defeated

298
00:34:40.610 --> 00:34:42.404
All the elites from the different countries.

299
00:34:42.404 --> 00:34:44.948
Today's arrangement was also his own wish.

300
00:34:44.948 --> 00:34:47.409
Mita-san.

301
00:34:48.535 --> 00:34:50.704
What is your real objective?

302
00:34:51.204 --> 00:34:52.748
Is this for the pride and honor of Japan?

303
00:34:52.748 --> 00:34:54.833
Or is it simply for your own wager?

304
00:34:56.418 --> 00:35:00.797
To me. what's really important is
the spirit of martial arts.

305
00:35:03.592 --> 00:35:05.677
We compete because we want to win.

306
00:35:21.193 --> 00:35:22.194
Let's begin.

307
00:35:22.694 --> 00:35:24.404
Yuan Jia. my brother.

308
00:35:25.072 --> 00:35:27.657
This competition is very unfair to you.

309
00:35:27.657 --> 00:35:31.161
If you choose another day for the fight
I have no objections.

310
00:35:33.705 --> 00:35:35.916
I understand your good intentions.

311
00:35:35.916 --> 00:35:38.418
But I am already standing in this arena.

312
00:35:38.418 --> 00:35:40.337
There must be a conclusion.

313
00:35:41.088 --> 00:35:42.089
Please!

314
00:36:00.148 --> 00:36:01.024
Start!

315
00:37:09.968 --> 00:37:11.178
Good. very good!

316
00:37:11.178 --> 00:37:13.638
Master is great!

317
00:37:57.432 --> 00:37:59.393
This round ends in a draw.

318
00:37:59.393 --> 00:38:02.354
Let's wait and continue in the next round
with a empty-hand fight.

319
00:38:02.354 --> 00:38:04.648
Both sides please prepare yourselves.

320
00:38:07.818 --> 00:38:09.861
Mita. where have you been?

321
00:38:09.861 --> 00:38:11.196
We're going to lose.

322
00:38:11.196 --> 00:38:13.740
I have arranged everything.

323
00:38:13.740 --> 00:38:15.575
Don't worry gentlemen.
I have it under control.

324
00:39:10.172 --> 00:39:11.465
Yuan Jia!

325
00:39:23.894 --> 00:39:25.395
Stop!

326
00:39:25.812 --> 00:39:27.272
What happened?

327
00:39:27.272 --> 00:39:28.940
What are you doing Tanaka?

328
00:39:32.778 --> 00:39:33.987
Yuan Jia!

329
00:39:33.987 --> 00:39:36.740
Tanaka!
- Go now. go!

330
00:39:41.203 --> 00:39:43.872
Yuan Jia. what's wrong?

331
00:39:43.872 --> 00:39:45.082
What's the matter?

332
00:39:45.082 --> 00:39:47.751
I'm poisoned
- Poisoned?

333
00:39:48.168 --> 00:39:49.670
How did you get poisoned?

334
00:39:49.670 --> 00:39:52.005
What really happened?

335
00:39:52.005 --> 00:39:54.174
What are you doing?
- Water!

336
00:39:54.174 --> 00:39:55.550
Water?

337
00:39:55.550 --> 00:39:57.469
What happen to the water?

338
00:39:57.469 --> 00:39:59.680
The water was poisoned!

339
00:39:59.680 --> 00:40:00.931
They've already taken the evidence away!

340
00:40:00.931 --> 00:40:02.599
Yuan Jia. let's send you to the hospital!

341
00:40:02.599 --> 00:40:04.810
Master. let's go to the hospital!

342
00:40:04.810 --> 00:40:07.229
I've used too much strength.

343
00:40:07.229 --> 00:40:09.398
The poison has already spread throughout
my body. It's too late.

344
00:40:09.398 --> 00:40:12.609
Master. I'll find them and avenge you!

345
00:40:14.486 --> 00:40:16.446
Zhen Sheng!

346
00:40:17.656 --> 00:40:22.285
What you should be talking about
should not be getting revenge.

347
00:40:24.621 --> 00:40:29.292
Hatred will only breed more hatred.

348
00:40:30.544 --> 00:40:32.629
I don't want to see any enmity.

349
00:40:34.881 --> 00:40:38.343
The most important thing is to strengthen yourself.

350
00:40:38.510 --> 00:40:39.761
Yuan Jia.
- Master.

351
00:40:39.761 --> 00:40:41.638
Yuan Jia. let's stop the fight.

352
00:40:41.638 --> 00:40:44.266
I'll bring you to the hospital. let's go.
- Jing Sun!

353
00:40:47.436 --> 00:40:48.437
Jing Sun!

354
00:40:50.147 --> 00:40:52.983
I'm only a brute who knows how to fight.

355
00:40:54.026 --> 00:40:58.780
It took me many years just to realise
what martial arts really is.

356
00:40:59.614 --> 00:41:02.659
and what I can accomplish with martial arts.

357
00:41:03.118 --> 00:41:05.328
This competition is yet to be concluded.

358
00:41:06.163 --> 00:41:10.584
Man are unable choose how their lives begin.

359
00:41:12.336 --> 00:41:16.089
But they must have the courage to walk till their last step.

360
00:41:21.887 --> 00:41:23.305
Master.

361
00:41:23.680 --> 00:41:26.183
Tanaka! What came over you? Hurry up
and finish him with a strong blow!

362
00:41:26.183 --> 00:41:28.310
What do you mean?

363
00:41:28.310 --> 00:41:29.644
You need not ask so much.

364
00:41:29.644 --> 00:41:32.356
I must win this fight! Regardless of what the means are!

365
00:41:44.076 --> 00:41:45.786
Constantly strive to become stronger!

366
00:41:45.786 --> 00:41:47.746
Constantly strive to become stronger!

367
00:41:47.746 --> 00:41:51.416
Constantly strive to become stronger!

368
00:41:51.416 --> 00:41:56.088
Just watch.

369
00:42:15.857 --> 00:42:17.401
Stop the fight.

370
00:42:17.401 --> 00:42:21.279
Living on is more important than anything else.

371
00:42:22.614 --> 00:42:30.914
Listen.
Living is never a single person's own affair.

372
00:42:33.166 --> 00:42:38.380
If we must fight. I will not hold back.

373
00:42:39.589 --> 00:42:41.341
That would be my honor.

374
00:44:43.463 --> 00:44:45.757
Master.

375
00:44:47.134 --> 00:44:49.553
He lost! Huo Yuan Jia lost!

376
00:44:49.553 --> 00:44:51.221
Go! Go! Faster!

377
00:44:51.221 --> 00:44:54.224
Go. go. make the announcement!

378
00:45:00.647 --> 00:45:03.025
Wait a second!

379
00:45:24.880 --> 00:45:25.922
Huo

380
00:45:25.922 --> 00:45:27.090
Yuan

381
00:45:27.090 --> 00:45:28.717
Jia

382
00:45:28.717 --> 00:45:30.052
Yuan Jia!

383
00:45:30.052 --> 00:45:33.722
Huo Yuan Jia
- Huo Yuan Jia

384
00:45:33.722 --> 00:45:35.223
Master!

385
00:45:35.223 --> 00:45:47.986
Huo Yuan Jia!
- Huo Yuan Jia!

386
00:45:48.111 --> 00:45:49.363
Master!

387
00:45:51.573 --> 00:45:53.033
Tanaka! You useless trash!

388
00:45:53.033 --> 00:45:54.576
Look at what you've done!

389
00:45:54.576 --> 00:45:55.660
I lost.

390
00:45:55.660 --> 00:45:57.829
Who says you've lost? Who saw it?

391
00:45:57.829 --> 00:45:59.998
I understood deep within myself.

392
00:45:59.998 --> 00:46:01.667
I was beaten convincingly.

393
00:46:01.667 --> 00:46:03.710
Who do you think you are?

394
00:46:03.710 --> 00:46:07.506
How can you decide on your own?
Are you fit to be a Japanese?

395
00:46:15.514 --> 00:46:17.641
Bastard!

396
00:46:17.641 --> 00:46:21.812
You're a shame to the Japanese.

397
00:48:25.977 --> 00:48:31.024
Huo Yuan Jia passed away
after he reached the hospital
at the age of 42 years

398
00:48:32.859 --> 00:48:35.987
After his death. his spirit in martial arts
continued to live on.

399
00:48:35.987 --> 00:48:39.074
Even till today. the Jing Wu School
has opened various branches.

400
00:48:39.074 --> 00:48:42.077
over fifty countries and territories
all over the world.

401
00:48:42.077 --> 00:48:46.873
The End.

